<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OpenRoaming Profile is about to expire</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#080D4A]">
<div class="container mx-auto px-8 pb-8 pt-[50px]">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[18px] p-6 shadow-md">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Your OpenRoaming Profile is about to expire</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
            Your profile will expire in {{ timeLeft }} days. <br>
            To renew your profile, please follow these simple
            steps:
        </p>
        <ol class="mt-2 text-lg list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Click
                <a class="font-bold text-[#7BBA29] underline"
                   href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_landing')) }}">here</a>
                to access OpenRoaming portal
            </li>
            <li>Login with your credentials</li>
            <li>Inside the portal download new profile</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">
            Thank you,<br>
            OpenRoaming Portal Support Team
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
